{"tid":583393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有請各位巴打入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-03-07T03:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T04:06:38.000Z","uid":174110,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"986e0a008fb5c1a40cb2626d6aa39775089c1fed","tid":583393,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/105417_a01899d59fb07c533720fa1403f15301.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F105417_a01899d59fb07c533720fa1403f15301.png&h=9544ac38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習大大等於共產黨等於中華人民共和國🇨🇳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又新時代又具特色<br />\n你地評下理 佢嘅思想係唔係好高級先<br />\n點解會有咁多負皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:習大大係我心中嘅紅太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時落嚟香港打大老虎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我愛習大大 定當擁護黨中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比起共產黨 我情願加入牧師淋兄弟會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f820e78373941aa36c6d82b85dfd11cc4f4518","tid":583393,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人？"},{"pid":"f65a158a0584961a895d3925e4f5068a8c362a02","tid":583393,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74f820e78373941aa36c6d82b85dfd11cc4f4518","tid":583393,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"